 <h2>Suggestions for Diabetes Prediction</h2>

 <ul>

 <li><strong>Healthy Lifestyle Changes:</strong> Incorporate regular physical activity, a balanced diet, and

 stress management techniques into your daily routine.</li>

 

 <li><strong>Regular Monitoring:</strong> Keep track of blood glucose levels, blood pressure, cholesterol,

 and body weight. This helps identify early signs of diabetes.</li>
<li><strong>Early Medical Consultation:</strong> Seek medical advice if you notice symptoms like

 excessive thirst, frequent urination, or fatigue.</li>

 

 <li><strong>Education and Awareness:</strong> Learn about diabetes risk factors and prevention methods. 

 Stay informed through credible resources.</li>

 </ul>

